snippet.title: Ignition gameplay (PC Game, 1997)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Ignition (aka fun tracks), Dos PC game produced by Virgin Interactive in 1997 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/ignition/1738/
Racing first five levels of this crazy game... Choosing police cars and try to reach first place.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
